videos.headline: Kentucky gets pick-sixes on consecutive drives
videos.description: Kelvin Joseph puts Kentucky on the board first with a 41-yard interception return, and Jamin Davis adds another TD with his 85-yard return.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Highlight (Joseph and Davis get pick-sixes on consecutive drives for UK) 2020/10/17 ESHEET

videos.headline: Chandler gets the Vols on the board
videos.description: Tennessee finally breaks through the Kentucky defense as Ty Chandler powers his way into the end zone for a 4-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Chandler gets the Vols on the board) 2020/10/17 ESHEET

videos.headline: Tennessee WR kicks Kentucky defender below the belt after play
videos.description: Tennessee's Ramel Keyton delivers a low blow on defender J.J. Weaver after being tackled.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Tennessee WR kicks Kentucky defender below the belt after play) 2020/10/17 ESHEET

videos.headline: Kentucky extends lead with a 2-yard rushing TD
videos.description: Chris Rodriguez Jr. gets his head down and muscles his way into the end zone for another Kentucky touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Kentucky extends lead with a 2-yard rushing TD) 2020/10/17 ESHEET
